<div class="modal fade" id="help-modal" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="edit-churchgoer-modal" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-scrollable">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">How to Bulk Register Using a CSV File</h5>
        <button type="button" class="btn-close" data-bs-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close"></button>
      </div>

      <div class="modal-body">
        <div class="mb-5">
          <h6>Step 1: Downloading the Template</h6>
          <p>Registering multiple users requires a CSV file with a specific format like so:</p>
          <table class="table table-sm">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                <th scope="col">phonenum</th>
                <th scope="col">lastname</th>
                <th scope="col">firstname</th>
                <th scope="col">birthdate</th>
                <th scope="col">...</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr>
                <td>09170001111</td>
                <td>Dela Cruz</td>
                <td>Juan</td>
                <td>01/01/2000</td>
                <td>...</td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>09350001111</td>
                <td>Trinidad</td>
                <td>Andres</td>
                <td>12/31/2000</td>
                <td>...</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
          <p>You can download a CSV template by clicking the
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm download-template">
              Download
            </button>
            button below
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-5">
          <h6>Step 2: Filling up the rows</h6>
          <p>The template already has examples on to fill each column, but these are to note:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Dates must be in a format of dd/mm/yyyy</li>
            <li>If the person is <span class="baptism m-0">Unbaptized</span>, there is no need to fill up the baptismdate and baptismlocation fields</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="mb-5">
          <h6>Step 3. Uploading the File</h6>
          <p>Save your changes to the CSV file and upload it. After, only then you can click the <button type="button" class="btn btn-dark btn-sm">Bulk Registration</button> button</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h6>Step 4. You're Done! :D</h6>
          <p>You can go to the <a href="/loadMembers">Churchgoers page</a> to see if it worked right after!</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary download-template">Download CSV Template</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>